#   Named Individuals
############################

# Individual: <http://usefulinc.com/ns/doap#> (<http://usefulinc.com/ns/doap#>)

ObjectPropertyAssertion(<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker> <http://usefulinc.com/ns/doap#> _:genid2147483648)


ClassAssertion(<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Person> _:genid2147483648)
ObjectPropertyAssertion(<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox> _:genid2147483648 <mailto:edd@usefulinc.com>)
